            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01DsK34Xh7pTf3SBrD8cSWh1\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01M74Aek3v3BZYXnS4f3PCBy\",\"name\":\"extract-2\",\"input\":{\"text\":\"Perfect! We've captured all the core information about Friend of the Pod. Now let's personalize the look and feel of your page!\\n\\nOn the left side of your screen, you'll see the **Brand Personalization panel**. This is where you can add visual elements to make your project uniquely yours. Here's what you can customize:\\n\\n**Logo:** Upload your brand's logo (PNG, JPG, or SVG) by dragging and dropping or clicking to select from your computer.\\n\\n**Colors:** Choose a color palette that fits your brand. Pick from pre-defined schemes or create your own custom palette.\\n\\n**Social Links:** Add links to your social media pages (Twitter, Instagram, YouTube, etc.) so visitors can easily find you.\\n\\n**Images:** Upload any specific photos or graphics you'd like us to use in your design.\\n\\nAll of these steps are completely optional—feel free to skip any you're not ready for. When you're done personalizing (or if you'd prefer to skip ahead), you can click the **\\\"Build My Site\\\"** button to start building your page right away!\\n\\nWhat would you like to customize first?\"}}],\"stop_reason\":\"tool_use\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2789,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":280,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
